title: 10 Ambiguous Questions Yet to be Answered in AHS Apocalypse
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Now honestly where the hell is Kyle Spencer , I thought he became the butler of Miss Robichaux’s Academy coven. But they didn’t reveal his whereabouts and where did he go? Did he ran off or killed by coven witches?  Or something else, cuz his absence really bothered me in all the coven school scenes. There’s no logic to that.
Honestly I think we’re gonna get a sequel to apocalypse Bc this season should have been longer

Typical Ryan Murphy. He's done the same thing with every one of his shows. He opend up all these potentially fascinating storylines, then runs out of time and rushes to tie up as many loose ends as he can. Frustrates the heck out of me.
Miss Meade is the rubber man lmaao
